Package com.mycompany.anothercam

Class User

java.lang.Object
com.mycompany.anothercam.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
Staff, Student
public abstract class User extends Object
Represents the User Object and the following mutator methods. A user would be associated to the Student and Staff class.
